                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Aura Strength increases the effect of your aura on everyone. Aura Effectiveness increases the effect of everyone's auras on yourself."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "source": "local-wiki-sqlite",
                  "pageTitle": "Coaction Drift",
                  "pageId": 863988,
                  "revisionId": 2786890,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "When maxed, this will increase your aura's strength to (1 + 15%) ^ 2 = 1.3225x for yourself, and 1.15x for everyone else."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "source": "local-wiki-sqlite",
                  "pageTitle": "Coaction Drift",
                  "pageId": 863988,
                  "revisionId": 2786890,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "For example, when combined with Steel Charge , it will increase your melee damage by 1.3225 × 60% = 79.35% , and increase your squadmates' melee damage by 1.15 × 60% = 69% ."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
